message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs. Given its quality and functionality, it's valued at $100 by many of our customers. Considering its worth and the benefits it offers, I would like to propose a price of $95 for this exceptional product. This offer allows you to enjoy its full value while also making it more accessible to you. I believe this is a fair deal that benefits both of us. Please let me know if you're interested in proceeding with this offer.
